PrecisAuthority for the Minister of Transport to enter into an AGREEMENT with the STEPHENVILLE AIRPORT CORPORATION INC. to contribute an amount of up to $2,244,000 towards the cost of resurfacing Runway 09-27 at the Stephenville Airport, in the Province of Newfoundland.

precis:
Authority for the Minister of Transport to enter into an AGREEMENT with
the STEPHENVILLE AIRPORT CORPORATION INC. to contribute an amount of up
to $2,244,000 towards the cost of resurfacing Runway 09-27 at the
Stephenville Airport, in the Province of Newfoundland.
